Invocation Name: joker inspiration
des:
Start your day with an inspirational list of quotes from the Joker. The world is too serious to take it seriously, bring some fair chaos in your inspirations.
When using the skill, you can say "Alexa, next" to move to the next quote. At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the skill.
